      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>The moment the construct goes down a small man emerges out of hiding. He walks around the dead machine, examining it with childlike curiosity, then looks at you.

“It's dead,” the man informs you, like a physician offering his expert medical opinion.</npc_text>
