    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Bentanagbal,” says the man, bowing his head. “A loremaster extraordinaire.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What are you doing here, Bennie?”</text>
          <def_link>2</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>1</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“I was exploring,” says the man, nodding twice. “Our mechanical friend didn’t like it and chased me into a maintenance hole. A fascinating mechanism, don’t you think?”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“How long have you been here?”</text>
          <def_link>3</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>2</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Thirty seven days,” says the man instantly. “Eight hundred and ninety two hours.” He smiles awkwardly and nods again.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“How did you survive?”</text>
          <def_link>4</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>3</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Rats. It’s not ideal,” the man grimaces as if not sure he can recommend it to you, “but more than sustainable.” He nods again.

“They don’t taste as bad as you’d think. Very pungent, like a rabbit. Definitely sustainable.” Another nod.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What do you know about this place?”</text>
          <def_link>5</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>4</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“This place? I didn’t get very far.” He shakes his head for emphasis.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Why did you come here in the first place? What do you seek here?”</text>
          <def_link>6</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>5</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“A spear,” the man says reluctantly. “To reclaim my father’s throne.” He straightens up, trying to look the son of a man who once sat on a throne.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Must be some kind of spear, eh, Bennie?”</text>
          <def_link>8</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“What happened to your father?”</text>
          <def_link>7</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>6</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“They killed him,” says the man, looking down as if ashamed. “My brothers too. They killed everyone but me. And now I have to find the spear.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Tell me about this spear.”</text>
          <def_link>8</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>7</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“It’s called the Divine Spear. It is said that whoever wields it will not be denied. I need it,” he says simply as if it explains everything.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“Where are you from?”</text>
          <def_link>9</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>8</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“East,” says the man, suddenly tight-lipped. “Months of travel.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“So you’re going to grab that spear, march back home and demand what’s rightfully yours?”</text>
          <def_link>10</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>9</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>The man looks down again, then nods. “I have to.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“You don’t strike me as a fighting man.”</text>
          <def_link>11</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>10</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“That’s why I need the spear. Nothing can stand against it.”

He hesitates, then says, “If you promise to help me find the spear, I’ll help you get past these constructs.”</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“There is more than one?”</text>
          <def_link>12</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>11</UID>
    </dlgPart>
    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“A *lot* more,” says the man, nodding several times. It’s hard to say if he’s exaggerating or not.</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>“If you know a way to get past them, why did you spend a month eating rats in a maintenance hole?”</text>
          <def_link>13</def_link>
          <checkOnAppear />
          <checksOnClick />
          <linksOnClick />
          <scriptsOnClick />
        </dlgAnsw>
      </answers>
      <UID>12</UID>
