    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>“Ah!” says the man, looking smug for a change. “These constructs don’t attack each other. Why? Because they know that another construct isn’t a threat. How do they know it, you ask? I'll tell you if you agree to find the spear for me.”</npc_text>
